<h2 id="an-invitation-to-hexaflexagate">An invitation to hexaflexagate</h2>
<div class="pictures-container">
 <img src="../images/outreach/hexa1.jpg" class="shrinkToFit" height="250" />

 <img src="../images/outreach/hexa2.jpg" class="shrinkToFit" height="250" />

 <img src="../images/outreach/hexa3.jpg" class="shrinkToFit" height="250" />
</div>
<p>A  strip of paper and a bit of cello tape is all one needs to construct a <i>hexaflexagon</i>. Questions of a mathematical nature arise when you begin to examine the properties of your creation. And the answers to these questions may lead to new construction ideas!</p>

<p>For the sides to this talk <a href="../images/slides/hexaflexagons.pdf">click here</a>.</p>

